  <brief_title>Time Interval for Changing Closed System Suction Catheters, Effect on Ventilator Associated Pneumonia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Endotracheal Suction With or Without Daily Changes of Closed System Suction. Effect on Ventilator Associated Pneumonia and Cost</official_title>
